<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>ABOUT & LORE</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Our Story & World</div>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <img src="/ressources/who.png" alt="Profiteers poster" style="margin: 20px auto; width: 100%; "class="image-placeholder"/>
        <p>
            Profiteers PMC is the largest LGBTQ+ Arma 3 unit, bringing together players from around the world
            who share a passion for tactical gameplay and inclusive community values.
        </p>
        <p>
            Founded on principles of equality and respect, we've built a space where everyone can enjoy
            military simulation gaming without discrimination or toxicity.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>Our World: Lore & Background</h2>
        <img src="/ressources/mercenarynews.jpg" alt="Profiteers engaged as a mercenary group" style="margin: 20px auto; width: 100%;" class="image-placeholder"/>
        <h3>The Setting</h3>
        <p>
            In a world where governments are collapsing and riots shake entire nations, private military
            companies have risen to fill the power vacuum. Profiteers PMC operates in this chaotic landscape,
            taking contracts from whoever can pay.
        </p>
        
        <!-- <h3>Our Story</h3>
        <p>
            <em>[Add your custom lore here - this is where you can detail the unit's backstory,
            major operations, character development, and the evolving narrative created by your community]</em>
        </p>
        
        <p>
            Our campaigns are shaped by custom lore written by multiple community members. As you participate
            in operations, you'll discover pieces of this living narrative woven directly into the missions.
        </p> -->
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>Community Values</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-3">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🏳️‍🌈 Inclusive</h3>
                <p>LGBTQ+ friendly and welcoming to all. We don't tolerate hate or discrimination of any kind.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>⚖️ Equal</h3>
                <p>No ranking systems. Everyone has an equal voice and equal opportunities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🎭 Creative</h3>
                <p>Community-driven storytelling and mission creation. Your ideas shape our world.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

